(self.webpackChunkcasdoor_website=self.webpackChunkcasdoor_website||[]).push([[8122],{249:function(i){"use strict";i.exports=JSON.parse('{"blogPosts":[{"id":"welcome","metadata":{"permalink":"/ko/blog/welcome","editUrl":"https://github.com/casdoor/casdoor-website/tree/master/blog/2021-08-24.mdx","source":"@site/i18n/ko/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2021-08-24.mdx","title":"Welcome","description":"Welcome to Casdoor official website!\ud83d\udc4b","date":"2021-08-24T00:00:00.000Z","formattedDate":"2021\ub144 8\uc6d4 24\uc77c","tags":[{"label":"Casdoor","permalink":"/ko/blog/tags/casdoor"},{"label":"SSO","permalink":"/ko/blog/tags/sso"},{"label":"Authentication","permalink":"/ko/blog/tags/authentication"},{"label":"OAuth2.0","permalink":"/ko/blog/tags/o-auth-2-0"},{"label":"Casbin","permalink":"/ko/blog/tags/casbin"}],"readingTime":0.945,"truncated":false,"authors":[{"name":"ErikQQY","title":"Casbin Member","url":"https://github.com/ErikQQY","imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/52615090?s=120&v=4"}]},"content":"Welcome to Casdoor official website!\ud83d\udc4b\\n\\n## What is Casdoor?\\n\\nCasdoor is a UI centralized authentication / [Single-Sign-On(SSO)](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Single_sign-on) platfrom based on OAuth 2.0 / OIDC.\\n\\nCasdoor is developed by [Casbin](https://casbin.org) using Golang and JavaScript.\\n\\nCasdoor aims at providing a powerful authentication platform to handle the users management.\\n\\n## Why use Casdoor?\\n\\n* \u26a1\ufe0f Powerful feature and simple config. With support for  <img src=\\"https://cdn.casbin.org/img/social_google.png\\" width=\\"30\\"></img> <img src=\\"https://cdn.casbin.org/img/social_github.png\\" width=\\"30\\"></img> <img src=\\"https://cdn.casbin.org/img/social_facebook.png\\" width=\\"30\\"></img> <img src=\\"https://cdn.casbin.org/img/social_twitter.png\\" width=\\"30\\"></img> <img src=\\"https://cdn.casbin.org/img/social_linkedin.png\\" width=\\"30\\"></img> <img src=\\"https://cdn.casbin.org/img/social_weibo.png\\" width=\\"30\\"></img> <img src=\\"https://cdn.casbin.org/img/social_wechat.png\\" width=\\"30\\"></img> <img src=\\"https://cdn.casbin.org/img/social_qq.png\\" width=\\"30\\"></img> <img src=\\"https://cdn.casbin.org/img/social_dingtalk.png\\" width=\\"30\\"></img>   <img src=\\"https://cdn.casbin.org/img/social_gitee.png\\" width=\\"30\\"></img>  <img src=\\"https://cdn.casbin.org/img/social_wecom.png\\" width=\\"30\\"></img><img src=\\"https://cdn.casbin.org/img/social_gitlab.png\\" width=\\"30\\"></img> sign in and traditional username/password sign in, Casdoor helps you implement your users management system just in a few steps.\\n\\n* \ud83d\udca5 Front-end back-end separation architecture. Casdoor provides maneuverable web UI and supporting high concurrency.\\n\\n* \ud83e\udd42 Active open source community. Casdoor is open source and actively maintained.\\n\\n* \ud83c\udf10 Multi-language support. Casdoor supports multiple languages, including Chinese, English, French, and many more.\\n\\n\\n## How to use Casdoor?\\n\\nYou can follow the detailed document to learn about [Casdoor API](https://door.casbin.com/swagger/) and [setup your own Casdoor](/docs/basic/server-installation). Or use the [Casdoor SDK](/docs/how-to-connect/overview) to implement your own application."}]}')}}]);